animeDescription: I can dance! I can sing! So, I can speak English! Hello Cocomong is a series of musical episodes teaching kids through song and dance. A large amount of episodes are aimed to teach English to Korean speaking children, though the intention is lost with the official English dub of the show.
animeRelated: ['Parent story: Naengjang-go Nala Cocomong', 'Sequel: Hello Cocomong 2']
